PushingBox,is,cloud,notification,service,It,connects,an,array,of,users,digital,notification,services,such,as,email,Twitter,Toasty,and,more,to,receive,alerts,for,predetermined,actions,These,actions,are,called,scenarios,and,can,linked,to,anything,from,the,doorbell,ringing,to,receiving,emails,Their,API,exposes,the,integrative,functionality,of,the,PushingBox,service